                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1001877989" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1001877989">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/jqcx/">焚琴客</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-02-26</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">军政纷繁，云诡波谲，尽付于案牍奏疏之中，后之览者，殊可鉴焉。叙述抽丝拨茧，文风矫夭灵动，不愧才子之作也。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="875496178">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
